## CRITICAL RULES — READ BEFORE EVERY GENERATION

### Rule 1: Condition Count
- Each side (long/short) must have **EXACTLY 3, 4, or 5 conditions**.
- An RSI range filter (e.g., rsi gt 40 AND rsi lt 70) counts as **2 conditions**.
- Do NOT go below 3 conditions per side. Do NOT exceed 5 conditions per side.

